cs.AR, cs.PL, cs.CR, cs.SE, cs.DC 

This paper discusses weak memory models and their complexity in microarchitectures, which falls under the category of computer architecture (cs.AR). The paper also presents new models for weak memory, which involves programming languages (cs.PL) and software engineering (cs.SE). The paper also discusses the performance penalty of certain microarchitectures, which falls under the category of computer systems and networking (cs.CR) and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC).
